{{Unreferenced|date=January 2025}} [[File:UENO-oji Monument.JPG|thumb|Stone monument marking the site of Ueno Ōji]] '''Ueno Ōji''' (うえのおうじ) was the fourth shrine in the {{ill|Kumano Kyuju-kū Ōji|ja|九十九王子|lt=Ninety-Nine Ōji|1=Ninety-Nine Ōji|lt=Ninety-Nine Ōji|2=ja|3=九十九王子|lt=Ninety-Nine Ōji|4=fr|5=Kujūkuōji|1=Ninety-Nine Ōji|lt=Ninety-Nine Ōji|1=Ninety-Nine Ōji|lt=Ninety-Nine Ōji|1=Ninety-Nine Ōji|lt=Ninety-Nine Ōji|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kumano Kyuju-kū Ōji|13=User:Immanuelle/Ninety-Nine Ōji|lt=Ninety-Nine Ōji|qq=}} pilgrimage network. The shrine no longer exists.
A stone monument labeled "Site of the Upper Shrine" (上宮跡) stands under the eaves at the entrance of Uenomiyadai Heights, located in Uenomiyachō 4, [[:en:Tennōji-ku, Osaka|Tennoji-ku, Osaka]], [[:en:Osaka|Osaka City]]. This is believed to be the shrine's former location, though there is no conclusive evidence. Currently, Ueno Ōji is enshrined within {{ill|Oe Shrine (Osaka)|ja|大江神社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Oe Shrine (Osaka)|qq=}} (5-40 Yūhigaokachō, Tennoji-ku, Osaka).
In the past, it was part of the "Seven Shrines of [[:en:Shitennō-ji|Shitenno-ji]]" (四天王寺七社), serving as Uenomiyachō Shrine to protect Shitenno-ji. Nearby is {{ill|Uenomiya High School|ja|上宮高等学校|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Uenomiya High School|qq=}}.
== Nearest Stations == * '''Oe Shrine''': [[:en:Tanimachi Line|Tanimachi Line]] – [[:en:Shitennōji-mae Yūhigaoka Station|Shitennoji-mae Yuhigaoka Station]] or [[:en:West Japan Railway Company|JR West]] – [[:en:Tennōji Station|Tennoji Station]] * '''Stone Monument''': [[:en:Kintetsu Railway|Kintetsu Railway]] – [[:en:Ōsaka Uehommachi Station|Osaka Uehommachi Station]] == See Also == * {{ill|Kumano Faith|ja|熊野信仰|1=Kumano shrine|lt=Kumano Three Shrines|lt=Kumano faith|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kumano Faith|13=User:Immanuelle/Kumano Three Shrines|qq=}} * [[:en:Kumano Kodō|Kumano Kodō]] – {{ill|Kiiji Route|ja|紀伊路|1=Kiiji|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kiiji Route|13=User:Immanuelle/Kiiji|qq=}} * {{ill|Kumano Kyuju-kū Ōji|ja|九十九王子|lt=Ninety-Nine Ōji|1=Ninety-Nine Ōji|lt=Ninety-Nine Ōji|2=ja|3=九十九王子|lt=Ninety-Nine Ōji|4=fr|5=Kujūkuōji|1=Ninety-Nine Ōji|lt=Ninety-Nine Ōji|1=Ninety-Nine Ōji|lt=Ninety-Nine Ōji|1=Ninety-Nine Ōji|lt=Ninety-Nine Ōji|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kumano Kyuju-kū Ōji|13=User:Immanuelle/Ninety-Nine Ōji|lt=Ninety-Nine Ōji|qq=}} : {{ill|Kōto Ōji|ja|郡戸王子|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kōto Ōji|qq=}} – '''Ueno Ōji''' – {{ill|Abe Ōji Shrine|ja|阿倍王子神社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Abe Ōji Shrine|qq=}}
